  "title": "Cliona's Wave: A New Musical",
  "description": "Thorn &amp; Ivy Theatre is proud to present the world premiere of Cliona's Wave! Cliona's Wave chronicles a select group of tales of Irish folklore, told through song and dance. This musical comprises several original tunes, as well as a few traditional Irish ballads and Jigs. Grab your tap shoes, and don't miss out!",
  "credits": "<strong>Playwright</strong>: Ethan Bintu-Watt<br/><strong>Director</strong>: Ocean Pettigrew<br/><strong>Cast</strong>: Katie Moran, Kohen Foley, Malachi Short, Matthew Baba, Kevin Thomas, Zakary Matsuba, Ashlin Turcotte, Harmony Bhuee, Jenn Houle, Sophie Healey, Don Figueroa, Sophie Pickett, Ren Elliott, Autumn Chugg<br/>",
  "website": "https://instagram.com/thornivytheatre",
  "plain_language": "Cliona's Wave is an imaginative story that draws inspiration from traditional Irish folk tales. There is lots of music, dancing, and a fun time for all!",
